title: Experience The All-new Stillwater Regional Airport In Oklahoma (kswo): Your Landing Destination
description:
Stillwater Regional Airport (KSWO) has been updated in MSFS, enhancing the airport's details significantly. The airport houses the Oklahoma State University Flight Center, dedicated to training students pursuing majors or minors in Aerospace Administration and Operations, focusing on becoming professional pilots.
